<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><a href="/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/20150618監察院抓鬼_6660.jpg"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-681" src="/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/20150618監察院抓鬼_6660-1024x578.jpg" alt="" width="800" height="451" srcset="/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/20150618監察院抓鬼_6660-1024x578.jpg 1024w, /wp-content/uploads/2015/06/20150618監察院抓鬼_6660-300x169.jpg 300w, /wp-content/uploads/2015/06/20150618監察院抓鬼_6660.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" /></a></p>
